document.topic_text: Rângva sem MLA RL Pianmawia chuan, August 10, 2016 khan Darlawna BDO pisaah rangva a sem. Rangva hi Rural Housing Scheme hnuaia sem niin, mi 30 hnenah bundle li zela pek a ni a, bundle li chu Rs. 15,312 man a ni. A dawngtute'n Rs. 1,531 an chawi ve thung. Share this Post
